A basic directory structure with the folders for source code, test cases, and documentation for Milestone 2

UVSim/
│
├── src/
│   ├── UVSim.py                     # Main program file
│   ├── file_loader.py               # File input handling logic
│   ├── basicml_Instructions.py      # Instruction set implementation
│   ├── cpu.py                       # CPU logic and instruction execution
│   ├── memory.py                    # Memory management
│   └── accumulator.py               # Accumulator logic
│   └── command-Line_Interface.py    # Prompt user for input
│
├── tests/                           # Unit tests for individual components
│   ├── test_instructions.py         # Write unit tests BasicML instructions
│   └── test_file_loader.py          # Unit tests for file loading
│   └── unit_tests.py                # Implement unit tests for each component
│   └── tests1.txt                   # Test file 1 given to us
│   └── test2.txt                    # Test file 2 given to us
│
└── docs/                           # Documentation
│   ├── Meeting Reports             
│   └── Class Definition  
│   └── Class Diagram
│   └── Project Structure               
│   └── State transition diagram                   
│   └── Use Case Diagram                 
